doc.after: Swedes are among the greatest consumers of newspapers in the world and nearly every town is served by a local paper The country s main quality morning papers are Dagens Nyheter liberal G teborgs Posten liberal Svenska Dagbladet liberal conservative and Sydsvenska Dagbladet liberal The two largest evening tabloids are Aftonbladet social democratic and Expressen liberal The ad financed free international morning paper Metro International was originally founded in Stockholm Sweden The country s news is reported in English by among others The Local liberal
